<template><div><p>终端常用命令</p>
<div class="language-bash line-numbers-mode" data-ext="sh"><pre v-pre class="language-bash"><code><span class="token number">1</span>. **导航命令:**
   -  <span class="token variable"><span class="token variable">`</span><span class="token builtin class-name">cd</span><span class="token variable">`</span></span> <span class="token builtin class-name">:</span> 切换目录
   -  <span class="token variable"><span class="token variable">`</span><span class="token function">ls</span><span class="token variable">`</span></span> <span class="token builtin class-name">:</span> 列出文件和目录
   -  <span class="token variable"><span class="token variable">`</span><span class="token builtin class-name">pwd</span><span class="token variable">`</span></span> <span class="token builtin class-name">:</span> 显示当前工作目录
   -  <span class="token variable"><span class="token variable">`</span><span class="token function">mkdir</span><span class="token variable">`</span></span> <span class="token builtin class-name">:</span> 创建目录
   -  <span class="token variable"><span class="token variable">`</span><span class="token function">rmdir</span><span class="token variable">`</span></span> <span class="token builtin class-name">:</span> 删除目录

<span class="token number">2</span>. **文件管理命令:**
   -  <span class="token variable"><span class="token variable">`</span><span class="token function">touch</span><span class="token variable">`</span></span> <span class="token builtin class-name">:</span> 创建新文件
   -  <span class="token variable"><span class="token variable">`</span><span class="token function">rm</span><span class="token variable">`</span></span> <span class="token builtin class-name">:</span> 删除文件
   -  <span class="token variable"><span class="token variable">`</span><span class="token function">cp</span><span class="token variable">`</span></span> <span class="token builtin class-name">:</span> 复制文件或目录
   -  <span class="token variable"><span class="token variable">`</span><span class="token function">mv</span><span class="token variable">`</span></span> <span class="token builtin class-name">:</span> 移动或重命名文件或目录

<span class="token number">3</span>. **查看和编辑文件:**
   -  <span class="token variable"><span class="token variable">`</span><span class="token function">cat</span><span class="token variable">`</span></span> <span class="token builtin class-name">:</span> 显示文件内容
   -  <span class="token variable"><span class="token variable">`</span><span class="token function">more</span><span class="token variable">`</span></span>  或  <span class="token variable"><span class="token variable">`</span><span class="token function">less</span><span class="token variable">`</span></span> <span class="token builtin class-name">:</span> 逐页查看文件内容
   -  <span class="token variable"><span class="token variable">`</span><span class="token function">nano</span><span class="token variable">`</span></span>  或  <span class="token variable"><span class="token variable">`</span><span class="token function">vim</span><span class="token variable">`</span></span> <span class="token builtin class-name">:</span> 文本编辑器，用于编辑文件

<span class="token number">4</span>. **进程管理:**
   -  <span class="token variable"><span class="token variable">`</span><span class="token function">ps</span><span class="token variable">`</span></span> <span class="token builtin class-name">:</span> 显示进程信息
   -  <span class="token variable"><span class="token variable">`</span><span class="token function">kill</span><span class="token variable">`</span></span> <span class="token builtin class-name">:</span> 终止进程
   -  <span class="token variable"><span class="token variable">`</span><span class="token function">top</span><span class="token variable">`</span></span>  或  <span class="token variable"><span class="token variable">`</span><span class="token function">htop</span><span class="token variable">`</span></span> <span class="token builtin class-name">:</span> 显示系统进程和资源使用情况

<span class="token number">5</span>. **网络命令:**
   -  <span class="token variable"><span class="token variable">`</span><span class="token function">ping</span><span class="token variable">`</span></span> <span class="token builtin class-name">:</span> 检查网络连接
   -  <span class="token variable"><span class="token variable">`</span><span class="token function">ifconfig</span><span class="token variable">`</span></span>  或  <span class="token variable"><span class="token variable">`</span><span class="token function">ip</span><span class="token variable">`</span></span> <span class="token builtin class-name">:</span> 显示网络接口信息
   -  <span class="token variable"><span class="token variable">`</span><span class="token function">ssh</span><span class="token variable">`</span></span> <span class="token builtin class-name">:</span> 安全 Shell，用于连接远程服务器

<span class="token number">6</span>. **系统信息:**
   -  <span class="token variable"><span class="token variable">`</span><span class="token function">uname</span><span class="token variable">`</span></span> <span class="token builtin class-name">:</span> 显示系统信息
   -  <span class="token variable"><span class="token variable">`</span><span class="token function">df</span><span class="token variable">`</span></span> <span class="token builtin class-name">:</span> 显示磁盘空间使用情况
   -  <span class="token variable"><span class="token variable">`</span><span class="token function">free</span><span class="token variable">`</span></span> <span class="token builtin class-name">:</span> 显示内存使用情况

这些是终端中常用的一些命令。如果您需要更多具体的信息或对任何命令有疑问，请随时告诉我。
